-- Phylo: common food species seed
-- Run in the Supabase SQL editor.
--
-- Skips species already present (case-insensitive latin_name), matching index
-- species_latin_name_unique on lower(trim(latin_name)).
--
-- Cultivar/subspecies entries are separate where noted; same-species foods are
-- merged with alternative_names (e.g. portobello + button mushroom, edamame + soybean).

